You want to get into 3C

260
00:42:17,400 --> 00:42:19,360
because it's a money laundering hub
for Fire Phoenix.

261
00:42:21,800 --> 00:42:24,720
Dhammatat, you can still back out

262
00:42:25,400 --> 00:42:26,400
if you don't want
to get caught up in this.

263
00:42:26,480 --> 00:42:28,600
You're acting like we just met yesterday.

264
00:42:29,520 --> 00:42:31,880
You know that risky stuff

265
00:42:31,960 --> 00:42:34,120
always gets my instincts going.

266
00:42:34,760 --> 00:42:36,480
I have to get into 3C.

267
00:42:36,560 --> 00:42:39,080
No matter who tries to stop me.

268
00:43:01,720 --> 00:43:03,400
This brand is trending.

269
00:43:03,480 --> 00:43:06,400
I think it would be perfect
for the new uniform you want.

270
00:43:08,080 --> 00:43:11,160
I already have a brand in mind.
The one you chose is too basic.

271
00:43:11,840 --> 00:43:14,640
What kind of style do you want?
I can help find it for you.

272
00:43:15,600 --> 00:43:17,320
Smart and elegant.

273
00:43:18,680 --> 00:43:21,040
Both smart and elegant.

274
00:43:21,120 --> 00:43:23,160
That's a good choice.
Perfect for our company.

275
00:43:26,200 --> 00:43:27,920
How about this brand?

276
00:43:32,320 --> 00:43:35,120
The designer, who's the father,
just passed away.

277
00:43:35,200 --> 00:43:36,760
<i>Now, his son is taking over.</i>

278
00:43:36,840 --> 00:43:39,320
<i>I heard he's also started</i>
<i>a women's clothing brand.</i>

279
00:43:47,720 --> 00:43:48,600
Nun!

280
00:44:05,720 --> 00:44:06,680
What's his name?

281
00:44:06,760 --> 00:44:09,280
Mr. T, Taiga.

282
00:44:20,280 --> 00:44:23,680
{\an8}3C Group, let's see
how I'm going to crush you.

283
00:44:25,760 --> 00:44:27,760
{\an8}If you tarnish my family's name,

284
00:44:28,440 --> 00:44:29,520
{\an8}you won't get a single penny.

285
00:44:31,920 --> 00:44:34,840
{\an8}I will kill its members one by one
until I reach the big boss.

286
00:44:40,920 --> 00:44:42,840
{\an8}It's good to finally meet you, Taiga.

287
00:45:13,600 --> 00:45:17,760
Subtitle translation by:
Chomchanach Yanaharn

